  personSpokenTo: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3a6d4684b84495b4194f2e590137ad0c, type: 2}
  delayBetweenMessages: 0
  lines:
  - Already aware of the earlier findings from your peer, and that you understand
    the plan.
  - I have further information for you.
  - 'We infiltrated your coworkers home, he appeared to have been absent some days
    now. '
  - 'Having his web browser enabled allowed us to access the full government website. '
  - "The cultists are planning a ritual with the dome\u2019s citizens, cultivated
    ever since the days of the massacre."
  - And the lie of the virus was the perfect way to shepherd them all into it.
  - (Website Available In Your Web Browser)
  - Take a look for yourself if you wish.
  - 'Regarding the attack we have planned, expect a knock on your door within the
    next short while. '
  - "We\u2019ll have someone that escorts you to a safe location so that we can carry
    it out."
